OL,5, A police officer who was driving a van 
OL,6, that struck and killed an 80-year-old  
OL,7, man has been advised they are under    
OL,8, criminal investigation.                
OL,10,FTrevor Bartlett was hit by the police  
OL,11,Fvan on the A52 Derby Road in Beeston,  
OL,12,FNottinghamshire, on 19 December.       
OL,14,FThe Independent Office for Police      
OL,15,FConduct (IOPC) has been investigating. 
OL,17,FIt has established the officer was     
OL,18,Ftaking a detainee to a custody facility
OL,19,Fand was travelling in a bus lane with  
OL,20,Fblue lights and sirens activated.      
